<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dizzy2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dizzy,</orth> vb. to make giddy, to stun: <cit><quote>d. with more clamour Neptune's ear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.2.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 2, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>would d. the arithmetic of memory,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 119</bibl></cit>.
